3-04/</link><description>法国占多数的议员在一项新法案中提议，对中国 Shein 等产品周转速度超快的时尚品牌应处以最高其服装售价 50% 的罚款，以抵消其对环境的影响。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 18:13:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/france-mulls-penalties-rein-ultra-fast-fashion-brands-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>联合国人权事务高级专员称中国在新疆和西藏实施侵犯人权行为</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/un-rights-chief-says-china-committing-violations-xinjiang-tibet-2024-03-04/</link><description>联合国人权事务高级专员沃尔克·特克周一呼吁中国落实建议，修改侵犯基本权利的法律，包括在新疆和西藏地区。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 13:05:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/un-rights-chief-says-china-committing-violations-xinjiang-tibet-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国长电科技将收购西部数据闪存工厂股权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/jcet-buy-80-stake-sandisk-chinas-unit-2024-03-04/</link><description>中国芯片组装和测试公司长电科技集团周一表示，计划以约 6.24 亿美元现金收购西部数据公司旗下上海一家闪存工厂 80% 的股权。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 12:47:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/jcet-buy-80-stake-sandisk-chinas-unit-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：鲍威尔在望，股市保持纪录，日经指数突破 40,000 点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-03-04/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 11:03:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国电池巨头宁德时代拟在香港设立研发中心以支持技术出口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-battery-giant-catl-looks-set-up-rd-centres-hong-kong-underpin-technology-2024-03-04/</link><description>中国电池巨头宁德时代董事长周一告诉记者，该公司正在讨论在香港设立研发中心，以创造可在海外和行业内获得许可的新技术。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 10:35:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-battery-giant-catl-looks-set-up-rd-centres-hong-kong-underpin-technology-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>华友钴业董事长提出电池材料政策化解产能过剩</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-huayou-cobalt-chief-proposes-battery-material-policy-tackle-overcapacity-2024-03-04/</link><description>据官方媒体周一报道，浙江华友钴业董事长在中国年度人大会议之前提出，中国应采取措施解决锂电池材料行业产能过剩问题。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 10:14:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-huayou-cobalt-chief-proposes-battery-material-policy-tackle-overcapacity-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>克里提升了美国的气候声誉，但世界的信任仍然难以捉摸</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/kerry-bolstered-us-climate-reputation-though-worlds-trust-still-elusive-2024-03-04/</link><description>周三，约翰·克里准备辞去乔·拜登总统气候变化问题特使的职务，这将使美国在全球气候外交中处于更有利的地位，尽管世界舞台上对美国政策意图的不信任挥之不去。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 10:06:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/kerry-bolstered-us-climate-reputation-though-worlds-trust-still-elusive-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>碧桂园可能会申请法院命令以验证股份转让</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/country-garden-may-apply-court-order-validate-share-transfer-2024-03-04/</link><description>中国开发商碧桂园周一表示，在评估其离岸重组的进展后，将考虑是否有必要在稍后阶段向高等法院申请生效令。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 10:04:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/country-garden-may-apply-court-order-validate-share-transfer-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>能源部长表示欧盟不能关闭太阳能进口边境</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/eu-cannot-close-borders-solar-imports-energy-chief-says-2024-03-04/</link><description>欧盟能源政策负责人卡德里·西姆森周一表示，欧盟应该支持陷入困境的欧洲太阳能电池板制造商，但不能对此类产品的进口关闭边境。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 08:58:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/eu-cannot-close-borders-solar-imports-energy-chief-says-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>解说：本周中国两会的看点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/what-look-chinas-annual-parliament-session-this-week-2024-03-04/</link><description>中国议会、全国人民代表大会（NPC）将于周二召开年度会议，所有人的目光都集中在支持世界第二大经济体增长的计划上。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 07:54:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/what-look-chinas-annual-parliament-session-this-week-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>马科斯表示，如果海洋利益被忽视，菲律宾将反击中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-will-push-back-against-china-if-maritime-interests-ignored-marcos-2024-03-04/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯周一表示，菲律宾将在有争议的南海问题上与中国合作，但如果其主权和海洋权利被忽视，菲律宾将予以反击。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 07:43:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-will-push-back-against-china-if-maritime-interests-ignored-marcos-2024-03-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国结束30年传统：总理年度新闻发布会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-cancels-premiers-press-conference-first-time-since-1993-2024-03-04/</link><description>中国取消了其经济和政策日历上最受广泛关注的活动之一，即总理的会后新闻发布会，一些观察家认为此举表明该国日益内向和集中控制。</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 06:48:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-cancels-premiers-press-conference-first-time-since-1993-2024-03-04/</guid></item></channel></rss>